      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2020 sedan in poor condition. The exterior has significant scratches, dents, and visible wear throughout. Mechanically it runs but has multiple components that need repair or replacement in the near term. The interior shows considerable wear including staining and damage to seating surfaces. This vehicle requires substantial work and is priced accordingly.",
